dct_description_sm: Morocco. Direction de la Conservation Fonciere et des Travaux Topographiques. Relief shown by 5 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. In upper right margin of each sheet: sheet diagram. In lower right margin of sheet 2: "Projection conique conforme de Lambert: systeme nord Maroc". On verso of sheet 1: indices to points of interests for both sheets.
